    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 2000, 4000, 8000 - CHASSIS ACCESSORIES - DESCRIPTION - Air Dryer
        (Bendix AD-9)
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Air Dryer (Bendix AD-9)</title>
        <para>The function of the air dryer is to collect moisture and contaminants before air reaches the first
            reservoir, thus providing moisture-free air for the air brake system. The heater in the air dryer prevents
            freeze-up in the purge drain valve during cold weather operation.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
